+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        Presentation Layer                   |
|   - JavaFX / Console UI                                     |
|   - Input: start, destination, optional tags (e.g., "bank") |
|   - Output: best routes (shortest, fastest, landmark-based) |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                          |
                          v
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                       Application Layer                     |
|   - RouteFinderService                                      |
|       • Selects and runs algorithms (Dijkstra, A*, etc.)    |
|       • Applies sorting (MergeSort, QuickSort)              |
|       • Applies searching (landmarks, route filters)        |
|   - LandmarkService                                         |
|       • Handles metadata like tags, categories              |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                          |
                          v
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        Domain Layer                         |
|   - Core Classes:                                           |
|       • Graph, GraphNode, Edge                              |
|       • Landmark (with tags, metadata)                      |
|   - Algorithms:                                             |
|       • Dijkstra, Floyd-Warshall, A*, Greedy, DP            |
|       • Vogel, Northwest Corner (optional for time est.)    |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                          |
                          v
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        Infrastructure Layer                 |
|   - Data Loading:                                           |
|       • Load campus map adjacency list from JSON/CSV        |
|       • Parse Landmarks (buildings, banks, libraries)       |
|   - Distance Calculator                                     |
|       • From dataset or API (Google Maps if extended)       |
|   - Persistence Layer                                       |
|       • In-memory storage (for now)                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
